{"tid":1242302,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇hr人士解答下我呢一個問題","createTime":"2019-06-19T04:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T12:09:55.000Z","uid":246724,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e916201dc4be1c48733c2ef081d61a361f671cd3","tid":1242302,"uid":246724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:06:35.000Z","msg":"我見某銀行啲trainee program，開頭hr話安排我見A部門。聽佢形容個po啲工作性質之後發現自己preference list其實都冇擺呢個，不過我都照見左先。成個過程就係普通panel in咁hr同dept head都係度，可惜之後一直無回音。<br />\n一個幾兩個月我77地打電話問status有另一個hr話肯幫我check，點知第二日call返過去佢答話pass左我個file去A部門。我問我上次唔係見左啦咩，然後佢同我講話我上次見嘅其實係B部門（我有擺落preference list嘅其中一個部門）。至於點解工作內容講成係A部門啲嘢，呢位hr話可能係佢同事搞錯。冇計冇offer咁梗係照狗衝照見。<br />\n但第二次in剩係得hr無manger一齊in，一黎就問我有冇其他offer，我答冇。之後問啲問題exactly同第一次一模一樣，hr全程好似無聽我講野咁一副hea樣。咁理所當然之後都係冇消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我係唔係比人玩左一鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29bcc03ac8213187bc8b0b8fe7f45ba1ee9534f","tid":1242302,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:09:13.000Z","msg":"hr換季啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95a0e4dc77c0eed500e6296d2b9786d44f94ef8","tid":1242302,"uid":158585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:10:31.000Z","msg":"有就有 無就無架啦 駛咩問"},{"pid":"4bcd42e7947ec6919fd136658a44b194b07d48b3","tid":1242302,"uid":182787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:12:37.000Z","msg":"MT program唔會得hr in"},{"pid":"de4e1fae1800fc2ff2fba950b06312c362e4e66a","tid":1242302,"uid":182787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bcd42e7947ec6919fd136658a44b194b07d48b3","tid":1242302,"uid":182787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:12:37.000Z","msg":"MT program唔會得hr in"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:17:52.000Z","msg":"戴返頭盔先, 唔知你邊間行, 但正常既MT program HR